00:01.490 --> 00:03.310
Previously on damages.

00:03.320 --> 00:08.330
Pulling the settlement now is
a move wherein tremendous risk...

00:08.570 --> 00:10.270
This is my legacy.

00:10.280 --> 00:12.040
I want my name back.

00:12.050 --> 00:13.350
I want redemption.

00:13.360 --> 00:16.340
I met a guy down in florida.

00:16.350 --> 00:18.580
Gregory turns out to
be our missing link.

00:18.590 --> 00:23.050
Gregory malina dumped his frobisher
stock the exact day arthur frobisher did.

00:23.060 --> 00:26.120
I burned her as a witness.It's done.

00:26.130 --> 00:27.600
Do you hear me?I'm done!

00:27.610 --> 00:30.100
Patty hewes will be
looking to depose you.

00:30.110 --> 00:31.190
How's it all been going?

00:31.200 --> 00:33.070
Great.We had our first fight.

00:33.080 --> 00:36.960
The last thing I want is for
my job to come between us.

00:37.250 --> 00:41.270
I heard you telling that other doctor
that you were gonna go see a movie?

00:41.540 --> 00:46.320
I want you to know that we are doing everything
that we can to make your grandfather comfortable.

00:46.330 --> 00:48.470
I know.Thanks.

00:48.480 --> 00:50.680
I'm not available.

00:50.990 --> 00:53.060
I...I'm engaged.

00:53.070 --> 00:56.460
We can...play this any way you'd like.

00:57.520 --> 00:59.870
There won't be room for him and patty.

00:59.880 --> 01:03.080
With patty hewes,there's only...patty.

