01:24.040 --> 01:26.380
I didn't kill,david.

01:27.350 --> 01:29.540
Someone tried to kill me.

01:29.550 --> 01:33.830
But,ellen,there was no
other body in your apartment.

01:34.680 --> 01:36.940
I wasn't in my apartment.

01:56.290 --> 01:58.600
Did you identify the body?

01:58.610 --> 01:59.850
There was no body.

01:59.860 --> 02:03.330
Well,that's impossible.

02:07.340 --> 02:09.850
There are things that I...

02:09.860 --> 02:12.210
I can't talk about.

02:12.220 --> 02:15.170
Why not?

02:16.170 --> 02:18.450
It's about the case.

02:18.850 --> 02:21.740
The frobisher case?

02:25.290 --> 02:28.060
3 1/2 MONTHS EARLIER

02:28.590 --> 02:30.020
Is this seat taken?

02:30.030 --> 02:31.600
No,no.Go ahead.

02:35.260 --> 02:37.280
What happened to your face?

02:38.020 --> 02:41.440
Consulting,you know.It's
a contact sport.

02:41.960 --> 02:44.350
My friend dated a consultant.

02:44.360 --> 02:46.060
Major heartbreak.

02:46.070 --> 02:47.400
Sorry to hear that.

02:47.410 --> 02:48.680
Yeah.

02:49.230 --> 02:52.600
He lied to her,pretended he was married.

02:53.160 --> 02:56.670
Made up some shit about
a guy in a limousine.

03:01.910 --> 03:04.070
I'm here alone,gregory.

03:04.080 --> 03:07.290
So,what,you're katie's
lawyer friend,right?

03:07.300 --> 03:09.110
She asked me to come talk to you guys.

03:09.120 --> 03:10.660
Why didn't you?

03:10.670 --> 03:12.860
'Cause I didn't know
anything about your case.

03:15.730 --> 03:18.270
How is katie?I liked her.

03:18.280 --> 03:22.330
Is that why you lied to her,humiliated
her and got her to perjure herself?

03:22.340 --> 03:24.290
I have no idea what
you're talking about.

03:26.950 --> 03:29.500
Katie thinks someone put you up to this.

03:29.510 --> 03:32.370
Given the shape your face
is in,maybe she's right.

03:33.310 --> 03:34.860
Who's pulling your strings,gregory?

03:34.870 --> 03:37.030
Nobody.Is patty hewes pulling yours?

03:37.040 --> 03:38.530
Patty doesn't know I'm here.

03:38.540 --> 03:39.520
Bullshit.

03:39.530 --> 03:43.070
If she did,you'd be holding a
subpoena or facing criminal charges.

03:43.530 --> 03:45.080
For what?

03:45.430 --> 03:48.770
Obstruction of justice,conspiracy
to cover up a felony.

03:49.230 --> 03:51.820
You know,if you're
lucky,that's ten years.

03:51.830 --> 03:53.840
You people are amazing.

03:54.920 --> 03:58.150
Just give me a name,gregory.I'll
keep you out of this.

03:58.480 --> 04:01.070
So when I give you a
name,you won't come after me?

04:01.080 --> 04:03.810
Not if you give us a bigger fish.

04:06.620 --> 04:08.130
Barney.

04:08.710 --> 04:10.410
What's his last name?

04:10.420 --> 04:13.800
Rubble.Lives in
bedrock.Hell of a right hook.

04:18.529 --> 04:20.060
You got 24 hours.

04:20.070 --> 04:21.589
Till what?

04:22.110 --> 04:24.570
Until patty hewes finds out about you.

04:24.580 --> 04:29.030
And once that happens,we subpoena
you,and we do it the hard way.

