05:17.940 --> 05:19.890
Do you think gregory believed you?

05:20.710 --> 05:22.610
I don't know.He's kind of a mess.

05:22.620 --> 05:24.150
You mentioned katie.

05:24.160 --> 05:26.710
Yeah.But he's pretty hard to read.

05:26.950 --> 05:30.850
He kept acting like he was being watched,and
he may have reason to be paranoid.

05:30.860 --> 05:32.610
What makes you say that?

05:32.620 --> 05:36.150
He had a bruise on his face.Looked
like he'd been in a fight.

05:36.160 --> 05:37.310
Really?

05:38.400 --> 05:41.410
I don't understand why we
haven't just subpoenaed him.

05:42.130 --> 05:44.130
Well,it would be better
if he came in willingly.

05:44.140 --> 05:46.390
If we subpoena him,he could clam up.

05:46.400 --> 05:48.590
Do you think he'll talk to us?

05:48.600 --> 05:53.210
I think he's scared,and I think he may
feel guilty about what he did to katie.

05:53.850 --> 05:55.970
What about you?

05:56.430 --> 05:57.970
What do you mean?

05:59.060 --> 06:01.050
This was a big step.

06:01.060 --> 06:03.100
Approaching a witness...

06:03.110 --> 06:05.490
under false pretenses...

06:05.500 --> 06:08.280
offering protection you can't provide.

06:08.290 --> 06:11.020
Don't they teach that in law school?

06:13.200 --> 06:15.240
So now what?

06:15.560 --> 06:19.200
You don't hear from gregory
in 24 hours,we subpoena him.

06:19.460 --> 06:21.640
And in the meantime?

06:22.020 --> 06:25.920
Dinner,8:00 tomorrow night,my apartment.

06:27.180 --> 06:29.300
Don't be late.

06:29.310 --> 06:32.150
So let her subpoena you.You
knew this might happen.

06:32.160 --> 06:33.980
All you've got to do is tell the truth.

06:33.990 --> 06:36.570
Just leave out a few details.

06:37.060 --> 06:39.750
Here.What were you doing in florida?

06:39.760 --> 06:40.760
Vacationing.

06:40.770 --> 06:42.840
Why was the apartment in your name?

06:42.850 --> 06:44.330
I rented it with some friends.

06:44.340 --> 06:45.820
What about your job?

06:45.830 --> 06:49.230
Applied for a training program,discovered
i had a knack for consulting.

06:49.240 --> 06:50.950
So what's the problem?

06:52.700 --> 06:54.530
Something you want to say?

06:54.690 --> 06:56.520
I want to talk to him.

06:56.530 --> 06:59.050
He doesn't talk to
you.You know how it works.

06:59.060 --> 07:01.040
Look,he's the whole reason
I got pulled into this thing.

07:01.050 --> 07:04.470
I'm tired of protecting him.I
just want to talk to him.

07:06.080 --> 07:08.020
Hold this a second.

07:09.590 --> 07:11.960
My advice to you?

07:12.730 --> 07:15.940
Anytime you get the urge
to think for yourself?

07:16.840 --> 07:17.660
Resist it.

07:17.670 --> 07:19.100
I told you...

07:19.110 --> 07:21.130
I want my life back.

07:21.140 --> 07:22.590
This is your life.

07:22.600 --> 07:25.140
Throw that away for me,will ya?

07:29.350 --> 07:30.190
You want one of these?

07:30.200 --> 07:33.270
No,I'm good with my espresso,thanks.

07:36.400 --> 07:39.330
You look a little sleepy
there,partner.Everything all right?

07:39.810 --> 07:45.310
It's just a touch of insomnia and
pesky dreams-- nothing too worrisome.

07:46.250 --> 07:48.810
I got just the person for you,ray.

07:48.820 --> 07:53.020
I couldn't get a good night's sleep
through that whole government trial.

07:53.030 --> 07:55.480
This therapist did wonders for me.

07:55.490 --> 07:56.810
Doesn't matter
what you have--

07:56.820 --> 08:02.690
either bruxism,you know,hypnic
jerks,exploding head syndrome-- she's terrific.

08:03.240 --> 08:05.090
Trust me,seriously.

08:07.990 --> 08:09.420
So...

08:09.430 --> 08:11.860
at your son's basketball game...

08:11.870 --> 08:13.120
Last night.

08:13.130 --> 08:15.360
I'm sitting up in the stands with holly.

08:15.660 --> 08:20.380
Other parents are up there,you know,and
this woman about two rows behind me...

08:20.390 --> 08:22.210
she spits on me.

08:23.760 --> 08:25.610
Back of my head.

08:25.620 --> 08:27.800
And you'd like me to...

08:27.810 --> 08:28.720
what?

08:28.730 --> 08:33.360
All this woman knows about me is what she
reads in the newspaper or sees on television,

08:33.370 --> 08:37.120
and she hates me so much
that she can to spit on me?

08:38.960 --> 08:42.230
Look,I'm not exactly
a young man anymore.

08:42.500 --> 08:44.270
Worried about your legacy.

08:44.280 --> 08:46.900
Yeah,I'm not a monster,ray.

08:46.910 --> 08:49.310
I don't want to be remembered as one.

08:49.320 --> 08:51.140
So what are you proposing?

08:53.140 --> 08:55.320
a memoir.You know?

08:56.700 --> 09:02.280
Show these people the real me,the family
me,you know,the-the husband,the father.You know.

09:02.780 --> 09:04.940
Maybe,uh...I don't know.

09:04.950 --> 09:08.140
Show 'em a picture of my childhood home.

09:08.150 --> 09:10.100
You know,I grew up poor.

09:10.110 --> 09:12.930
Maybe a chapter on my dyslexia.

09:13.620 --> 09:16.500
You know,that's
actually a terrific idea.

09:16.940 --> 09:20.260
We'll set you up with a
publisher right after the trial.

09:20.270 --> 09:22.370
No.No,no,no.Now.

09:22.380 --> 09:23.510
Art,no,no,no.

09:23.520 --> 09:25.590
You do this now,

09:25.600 --> 09:30.260
people could perceive it as a sign
of desperation-- or worse,guilt.

09:30.270 --> 09:32.640
Not if we do it right.Just
get me a ghostwriter,

09:32.650 --> 09:34.950
somebody who has a lot of
experience in this sort of thing.

09:34.960 --> 09:38.200
You're gonna allow some complete
stranger to poke into your life?

09:38.210 --> 09:40.760
No,ray...he'll be working for me.

09:40.770 --> 09:42.910
He'll be working for the publisher.

09:42.920 --> 09:46.430
You'll never be able to
control the flow of information.

09:46.440 --> 09:49.670
First thing you know,they'll be down
in your basement digging for bodies.

09:49.680 --> 09:51.130
Hey,you know something?

09:51.140 --> 09:53.260
Set this up for me.

09:53.590 --> 09:56.040
- Get me a writer,and stop being an asshole.
- Art...

09:56.050 --> 09:58.040
You're being an asshole.She spat at me!

09:58.050 --> 10:00.350
You know something?She spat at me.

10:01.490 --> 10:03.590
In front of my kids.

10:06.450 --> 10:08.760
The book's a good idea.

10:11.470 --> 10:13.670
I can't wait to read it.

10:18.820 --> 10:20.500
Ellen?

10:22.280 --> 10:24.110
You still awake?

10:25.390 --> 10:29.410
Demonstrators say if the three buildings
behind them and one other come down this week,

10:29.420 --> 10:33.120
it could be a very long time before
anything goes up in their place

10:33.130 --> 10:36.070
because there are a number of lawsuits
against the atlantic yards project

10:36.080 --> 10:39.470
that could take months
or even years to decide.

10:39.480 --> 10:42.820
Daniel goldstein heads the group
develop don't destroy brooklyn.

10:42.830 --> 10:45.930
He is one of 13 homeowners
in federal court challenging

10:45.940 --> 10:49.170
the developers' use of eminent
domain to take away their homes

10:49.180 --> 10:52.490
where forest city ratner plans
to build an arena for the nets...

10:52.500 --> 10:56.240
Oh,I had the tv on.I must have left
this morning without turning it off.

10:56.250 --> 10:58.670
Well,I'm just glad that you're okay.

10:58.680 --> 11:01.580
Oh,hey,listen i forgot to tell you.

11:01.590 --> 11:05.460
Tomorrow night,patty asked
us to dinner at her place.

11:05.960 --> 11:07.560
You forgot?

11:07.570 --> 11:09.270
I know,I screwed up.

11:09.280 --> 11:11.250
It's our one night together.

11:11.260 --> 11:13.630
We were going to try
that new mexican place.

11:13.640 --> 11:15.840
I know,I'm sorry,babe.

11:15.850 --> 11:19.020
Well,who's gonna be there?

11:19.410 --> 11:22.040
I think it's just her and her husband.

11:22.050 --> 11:24.680
And us?Jesus,ellen...

11:24.690 --> 11:27.930
I know,maybe it'll be fun.They
have this great apartment.

11:27.940 --> 11:29.350
Ellen,after everything
that happened with katie,

11:29.360 --> 11:32.780
why would I possibly want to
socialize with patty hewes?

11:32.790 --> 11:34.140
She's my boss.

11:34.150 --> 11:37.310
She wants to meet you.What
am I supposed to say?

11:41.170 --> 11:42.970
I don't want to go.

11:42.980 --> 11:45.710
David,can you please do this for me?

11:50.460 --> 11:51.470
Fine.

11:55.010 --> 11:57.740
I'll be a couple more hours.

12:06.110 --> 12:08.350
Lila.Hey.

12:08.360 --> 12:10.540
The nurse at your station
said you'd be here.

12:11.540 --> 12:14.640
Well...is everything okay?

12:17.060 --> 12:20.060
I know when you guys discharged my
grandfather from the hospital last week,

12:20.070 --> 12:21.840
he was doing really great.

12:22.290 --> 12:25.360
But,uh,saturday night
things took a turn.

12:26.200 --> 12:28.630
Did you call the paramedics?

12:28.640 --> 12:30.080
Yeah.

12:30.370 --> 12:32.890
He was dead by the time they got there.

12:34.650 --> 12:36.510
Oh,my god.

12:37.310 --> 12:39.360
I-I'm so sorry.I...

12:39.370 --> 12:42.420
I've been so busy that
i didn't even hear.

12:42.790 --> 12:45.130
Is there anything that I can do?

12:45.140 --> 12:46.890
Actually...

12:47.450 --> 12:49.010
I hate to ask.

12:49.020 --> 12:50.360
What?

12:50.950 --> 12:54.580
There's all this medical equipment
in our apartment-- his machines.

12:54.590 --> 12:56.660
The nurse said that I could
sell them on craig's list,

12:56.670 --> 12:59.310
but I just don't know
what they're worth.

12:59.320 --> 13:01.340
Do you know what kind
of machines they are?

13:01.350 --> 13:04.340
I'm not sure.I'd need
someone to tell me.

13:05.660 --> 13:08.170
Do you think maybe
you could take a look?

13:10.690 --> 13:11.340
Lila...

13:11.350 --> 13:13.850
Look,I know I acted
inappropriately before.

13:13.860 --> 13:17.040
You're engaged.I respect that.

13:19.760 --> 13:22.400
I could just really
use your help right now.

13:29.190 --> 13:31.890
Well...where do you live?

13:37.260 --> 13:38.970
David conner's phone records.

13:38.980 --> 13:40.350
And?

13:40.680 --> 13:43.560
Someone called him a half dozen
times the night before he was killed.

13:43.570 --> 13:44.810
Who?

13:46.000 --> 13:48.780
Her name is lila dimeo.

13:56.690 --> 13:58.190
What's the occasion?

13:58.200 --> 14:01.440
The occasion,ray,is gratitude.

14:01.450 --> 14:02.640
Thank you.

14:02.650 --> 14:06.850
No,ray,thank you.16 years of service.

14:06.860 --> 14:12.460
Government trial-- head to head in a ring
with patty hewes and we're still standing.

14:12.810 --> 14:15.110
Miracles do happen.

14:15.120 --> 14:16.750
You're a good friend,ray.

14:16.760 --> 14:18.640
Thank you.

14:20.220 --> 14:22.690
means a lot to hear you say that.

14:23.830 --> 14:25.490
Bottoms up.

14:29.760 --> 14:33.090
What's the matter?What is it?

14:35.180 --> 14:37.910
Oh,goddamn it,man,what...

14:58.040 --> 15:00.920
Mr.Fiske,it's time to leave
for the frobisher meeting.

15:01.440 --> 15:03.770
Thank you,kitty.

15:11.710 --> 15:14.030
You talk to the sleep
therapist yet,buddy?

15:14.040 --> 15:16.870
No,no,I haven't had the time.

15:17.660 --> 15:19.940
Ray,you got dark circles
under your eyes,man.

15:19.950 --> 15:22.300
You're walking like a corpse.

15:22.610 --> 15:24.840
You should call her.

15:26.310 --> 15:27.620
Hey,owen.

15:27.630 --> 15:29.070
What's up,dad?

15:30.540 --> 15:32.810
So,have you heard from
the publisher or not?

15:32.820 --> 15:35.080
They chose your writer.

15:35.090 --> 15:36.110
Fella from yale.

15:36.120 --> 15:41.170
Writes fiction no one reads,but
he's one hell of a biographer.

15:42.170 --> 15:43.500
Fantastic.

15:43.510 --> 15:45.350
Yeah,it is.

15:45.360 --> 15:47.600
Look,I want you to know,

15:47.610 --> 15:52.090
the publisher intends to have you
talk about your current litigation.

15:54.110 --> 15:58.610
It won't be the sole focus of the
book-- you can still get your story out--

15:58.620 --> 16:03.680
but they're insisting that candid
insight into your company's collapse

16:03.690 --> 16:08.760
and your perspective on the ensuing
trials will be a major selling point.

16:09.180 --> 16:12.690
Now,obviously,you can still back out.

16:13.360 --> 16:15.700
Frankly,that would be my advice.

16:19.030 --> 16:20.590
No.

16:20.880 --> 16:22.880
I want to do this.

16:25.510 --> 16:27.450
I have to do this.

16:27.460 --> 16:30.010
Tread lightly,art.

16:33.430 --> 16:36.670
People need to know who I am,ray.

16:37.960 --> 16:40.190
Don't be afraid to put
your nose right in there.

16:41.290 --> 16:43.460
Inhale that.It's an incredible vintage.

16:43.470 --> 16:47.370
This is a 2001 cabernet merlot blend.

16:47.810 --> 16:50.210
Intense concentration.

16:52.290 --> 16:54.030
What do you think?

16:54.810 --> 16:59.760
Uh,yes.It's got a
fantastic concentration.

17:00.550 --> 17:03.780
Really,it'S...incredible.

17:05.589 --> 17:08.020
Do you like wine,david?

17:08.030 --> 17:10.390
Wine?Sure.

17:11.750 --> 17:15.950
Oh,come on,david,we had pinot
grigio the other night.What was that?

17:18.050 --> 17:19.819
I don't remember.

17:20.349 --> 17:22.180
Phil knows everything about wine.

17:22.190 --> 17:25.109
I only know two things Red and white.

17:32.120 --> 17:36.340
Your sister must know a lot about
wine,what with a restaurant and all.

17:40.080 --> 17:42.620
Yeah,she does.

17:43.370 --> 17:45.460
How is katie?

17:46.420 --> 17:47.660
Not good.

17:47.940 --> 17:49.770
Oh,I'm sorry to hear that.

17:49.780 --> 17:51.540
Please send her my best.

17:52.820 --> 17:54.780
don't beg.

17:56.280 --> 17:59.280
So how did you guys meet?

18:00.440 --> 18:02.900
You tell,phil.I always get it wrong.

18:02.910 --> 18:05.670
Not a romantic bone
in this woman's body.

18:05.990 --> 18:08.450
It was '94.I was working for
the indonesian government.

18:08.460 --> 18:11.300
I was in jakarta.I was
restructuring the national bank.

18:11.310 --> 18:13.660
She was walking through
the hotel lobby...

18:13.670 --> 18:16.060
I'm terribly sorry.Excuse me.

18:17.200 --> 18:20.240
It's dubai.The market
is just opening there.

18:20.250 --> 18:22.600
I'm sorry.Excuse me,please.

18:22.610 --> 18:24.970
Bob?Yes.

18:32.500 --> 18:34.550
So how did you two meet?

18:35.430 --> 18:39.290
Berger?Berber,it's with a B.

18:39.300 --> 18:40.700
George is fine.

18:42.030 --> 18:45.130
So,george,I hear you're a smart guy.

18:45.140 --> 18:47.520
I understand you're writing a novel.

18:47.530 --> 18:50.070
Yeah,that's right.

18:50.840 --> 18:52.770
That's very impressive.

18:53.150 --> 18:54.600
Thank you.

18:54.610 --> 18:55.920
So how does this work?

18:55.930 --> 18:57.970
Should I just start telling
stories about myself?

18:57.980 --> 19:00.180
Or do you want to ask me questions?

19:00.190 --> 19:02.140
It's up to us.

19:02.640 --> 19:08.090
Although I do have a couple things to get
started,just to understand some basics.

19:08.100 --> 19:09.330
Yeah,shoot.

19:09.580 --> 19:10.800
Okay?

19:14.650 --> 19:20.710
