it can also signify...

37:43.680 --> 37:45.980
a secret you're keeping.

37:45.990 --> 37:51.630
More specifically,your overwhelming
fear that people will find it out.

37:55.490 --> 37:59.130
What?What's going on,mr.Fiske?

38:00.380 --> 38:02.420
Tell me.

38:06.500 --> 38:08.450
Let it out.

39:18.620 --> 39:20.010
Remember me?

39:20.800 --> 39:21.870
From the other night?

39:21.880 --> 39:23.850
Of course,I remember you.

39:23.860 --> 39:25.690
I came to see if you were okay.

39:27.010 --> 39:29.010
I wanted to give you my number.

39:59.250 --> 40:00.380
Yeah?

40:00.390 --> 40:02.370
Your boy--
gregory malina?

