40:08.630 --> 40:10.340
Better do it quick.

40:31.180 --> 40:32.490
I need to talk to you.

40:32.850 --> 40:34.110
You can't be here.

40:34.120 --> 40:35.530
Ray?Who is it?

40:35.540 --> 40:38.980
It's the wrong address!Just
go back to sleep,mallory!

40:39.310 --> 40:40.750
You need to leave.You...

40:40.760 --> 40:42.940
Just give me five minutes,ray.

40:42.950 --> 40:44.680
Just give me five minutes.

40:44.690 --> 40:46.850
I-I've got a doberman.

40:47.150 --> 40:48.730
Please?

40:57.380 --> 40:58.910
Please?

41:11.130 --> 41:12.730
Ellen?

41:16.110 --> 41:17.770
Ellen?

41:44.770 --> 41:46.440
Ellen?

42:11.650 --> 42:14.240
Surprise.

42:14.980 --> 42:17.430
