42:30.160 --> 42:32.720
I guess I forgot to lock it.

42:33.080 --> 42:34.480
Right.

42:38.930 --> 42:40.910
Are you going to get in?

42:42.580 --> 42:45.010
What's the special occasion?

42:46.130 --> 42:48.010
I miss you.

43:04.490 --> 43:08.550
Look...I'm not proud of
it,but it's what david wanted.

43:09.770 --> 43:11.730
And last night,where were you?

43:12.450 --> 43:16.140
Here,at home.Why aren't you
talking to ellen parsons?

43:16.150 --> 43:17.270
Why should we?

43:17.280 --> 43:20.310
Because she's crazy...and jealous.

43:21.300 --> 43:23.080
This is ellen parsons.

43:23.090 --> 43:28.310
Stay away from my fiance or I
swear to god,I will come after you.

43:29.450 --> 43:31.670
You called david six times yesterday.

43:31.960 --> 43:35.340
